### Get all products (initially empty)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products

###

### Create a new product
POST http://localhost:8080/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Laptop",
  "description": "High-performance laptop",
  "price": 1200.50
}

###

### Create another product
POST http://localhost:8080/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Smartphone",
  "description": "Latest model smartphone",
  "price": 799.99
}

###

### Get all products (should have 2 now)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products

###

### Get product by ID (ID 1)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products/1

###

### Update product by ID (ID 1)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/products/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Gaming Laptop",
  "description": "High-performance gaming laptop with RTX 4080",
  "price": 2500.00
}

###

### Delete product by ID (ID 2)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/products/2

###

### Get all products (should only have the updated Laptop)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products
